Description: Roleplay Utils
        ==============
        
        This is a roleplay utilities program written in python with a qt user interface. 
        
        How To Use
        ----------
        
        After installing this you can
        
        Features
        --------
        
        - It has D3, D4, D6, D8, D10, D12, D20 and D100 as standard.
        - The ability to add new dice. 
        - It can show probability distribution of the dice.
        - Keeps a history of dice rolls.
        - Can read PDFs.
        
        ToDo
        ----
        
